abstract: WESTBURY, L.I., Sept. 23-- Vernon Dancer moved Lana Hanover through a narrow opening between trotters in the closing yards tonight and his daring drive brought the daughter of Hickory SmokeLatona Hanover a nose victory over Jamie's Beauty in the eighth annual Lady Suffolk Trot before 30,523 at Roosevelt Raceway.
